---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Romillie Hadeljo">
  <div class="bg-emerald-950 min-h-screen text-stone-200">
    <main class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-white mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <p class="text-emerald-200/60 mb-10 text-sm">Last Updated: May 27, 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">When you use our inquiry form, we collect personal information that you provide to us, including:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-300 space-y-2">
              <li>Name</li>
              <li>Email Address</li>
              <li>Proposed Stay Dates</li>
              <li>Personalized Message/Requirements</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">We use the information we collect solely to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-300 space-y-2">
              <li>Respond to your booking inquiries.</li>
              <li>Provide information about our services and availability.</li>
              <li>Improve our guest experience.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">3. Data Security</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">We use industry-standard services like EmailJS to handle form submissions securely. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">Our site uses EmailJS to process inquiries. By submitting a form, you acknowledge that your information will be transferred to EmailJS for processing in accordance with their Privacy Policy.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">5. Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:bahehdowski@gmail.com" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline underline-offset-4">bahehdowski@gmail.com</a>.</p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
